        "title": "Teruhito Sugawara Hadir di GIIAS",
        "title_english": "Teruhito Sugawara Present at GIIAS",
        "sub_title": null,
        "image": "assets/uploads/articles/Management_Hino_Bersama_Pembalap_Hino_Truk_Dakar_Rally_Teruhito_Sugawara.jpg",
        "description": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Pembalap Utama Hino Dakar Raly, Teruhito Sugawara Kembali Hadir di GIIAS.</b></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Jakarta, 22 Juli 2019</b> – PT. Hino Motors Sales Indonesia (HMSI) menghadirkan kembali pembalap utama Hino Team Dakar Rally, Teruhito Sugawara ke booth Hino Indonesia dalam ajang Gaikindo Indonesia International Auto Show (GIIAS) 2019. Teruhito Sugawara kembali menyapa dan berbagi pengalaman serta cerita mengenai keterlibatannya dalam rally paling ganas ini hingga dia berhasil menjadi juara dalam gelaran Dakar Rally. Dalam kunjugan keduanya ke Indonesia, setelah tahun lalu turut juga hadir di GIIAS. Teruhito Sugawara berbagi cerita ketika pertama kali terjun di Dakar Rally pada tahun 1997 sebagai mekanik ayahnya yang merupakan pembalap tertua di Dakar Rally&nbsp; dan tercatat dalam buku rekor dunia yaitu Yoshimasa Sugawara, 77 tahun.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hino Team Sugawara sendiri menambah rekornya yang cemerlang pada Reli Dakar tahun ini. Tim ini&nbsp; menurunkan dua kendaraan Hino500 Series atau New Generation Ranger dalam balapan yang sangat berat di Peru, Amerika Selatan. Teruhito Sugawara yang kaya pengalaman mengikuti lomba ini berhasil finis diperingkat kesembilan di kategori truk umum. Finis yang luar biasa ini dicapai ditengah persaingan yang ketat dan didominasi oleh truk – truk kelas berat dengan mesin yang lebih besar melampaui 10 liter. Selain itu Hino berhasil terus mempertahankan tradisi juara, dimana hasil Dakar Rally 2019 membuat Hino 10 kali berturut – turut juara di kelas under 10 liter dan tidak pernah gagal mencapai garis finish selama 28 tahun ke ikut sertaannya.<br></div><div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://sevva.id/hino/assets/uploads/articles/65ded5353c5ee48d0b7d48c591b8f430.jpg\" style=\"width: 809.889px; height: 540.114px;\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>Pembalap Hino Truk Dakar Rally Teruhito Sugawara Memperlihatkan Medali Dakar<br></i></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \">Hino Truck Dakar Rally merupakan kendaraan yang menjadi simbol QDR (Quality,Durability,Reliability) dari truk Hino. Kendaraan ini merupakan spirit dari continuous improvement yang Hino lakukan untuk mendapatkan kendaraan yang terbaik. Dimana truk yang keluar sebagai juara dalam Dakkar Rally, merupakan truk yang sama kualitasnya dengan yang diproduksi untuk kelancaran bisnis para pebisnis di Indonesia. Ini menjadi bukti prestasi Hino New Generation Ranger yang merupakan dasar truk dari Hino Dakar berhasil menjadi market leader medium duty truck di Indonesia selama 19 tahun terakhir ini di Indonesia.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://sevva.id/hino/assets/uploads/articles/2a79ea27c279e471f4d180b08d62b00a.jpg\" style=\"width: 828.889px; height: 552.785px;\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>Talkshow Pembalap Hino Truk Dakar Rally Teruhito Sugawara<br></i></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify; \"><i>“Hino turun di dakar rally menggunakan mesin dan transmisi yang sama dengan apa yang kami sediakan untuk kelancaran bisnis customer disini. Hino menjadi satu – satunya brand asal Jepang yang turut serta di kategori truk dalam Dakar Rally, serta menggunakan truk yang diproduksi masaal untuk balapan terganas ini,&nbsp; Untuk itu ini bukti kekuatan dan ketangguhan truk Hino”</i>, <b>tutup Hiroo Kayanoki, Presiden Direktur HMSI.</b></div></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>",
        "description_english": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Main Driver, Hino Dakar Raly, Teruhito Sugawara is back at GIIAS.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Jakarta, 22 July 2019</b> - PT. Hino Motors Sales Indonesia (HMSI) brought back the main Hino Team driver Dakar Rally, Teruhito Sugawara to the Hino Indonesia booth at the Gaikindo Indonesia International Auto Show (GIIAS) 2019. Teruhito Sugawara returned to greet and share experiences and stories about his involvement in this ferocious rally. until he won the Dakar Rally title. In their second visit to Indonesia, after last year also attended the GIIAS. Teruhito Sugawara shared his story when he first entered the Dakar Rally in 1997 as his father's mechanic who was the oldest racer in the Dakar Rally and recorded in the world record book, Yoshimasa Sugawara, 77 years old.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hino Team Sugawara himself added his brilliant record to the Dakar Rally this year. The team unloaded two Hino500 Series or New Generation Ranger vehicles in a very heavy race in Peru, South America. Teruhito Sugawara, who was rich in experience in this race, finished ninth in the general truck category. This extraordinary finish is achieved amid fierce competition and is dominated by heavyweight trucks with larger engines exceeding 10 liters. In addition, Hino managed to continue to maintain the champion's tradition, where the results of the 2019 Dakar Rally made Hino 10 times in a row champion in the under 10 liter class and never failed to reach the finish line for 28 years to participate.<br></p><div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://sevva.id/hino/assets/uploads/articles/65ded5353c5ee48d0b7d48c591b8f430.jpg\" style=\"width: 830.889px; height: 554.119px;\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>Hino Racer Teruhito Sugawara's Dakar Truck Shows a Dakar Medal<br></i></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Hino Truck Dakar Rally is a vehicle that is a symbol of QDR (Quality, Durability, Reliability) of Hino trucks. This vehicle is the spirit of Hino's continuous improvement to get the best vehicle. Where the trucks that come out as champions in the Dakkar Rally, are trucks that are of the same quality as those produced for the smooth running of business people in Indonesia. This is proof of the achievements of the Hino New Generation Ranger which is the basis of trucks from Hino Dakar to become the market leader in medium duty trucks in Indonesia for the past 19 years in Indonesia.</div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://sevva.id/hino/assets/uploads/articles/2a79ea27c279e471f4d180b08d62b00a.jpg\" style=\"width: 818.889px; height: 546.116px;\"></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <i>Hino Racer Teruhito Sugawara's Dino Rally Talkshow Talkshow</i></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i><br></i></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><i>\"Hino went down at the Dakar rally using the same engine and transmission that we provided for the smooth running of the customer's business here. Hino is the only Japanese brand participating in the truck category in the Dakar Rally, as well as using trucks produced in the past for the fiercest races.</i><br></div></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>",
