        "description_english": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px;\">Hino Customer Care Center 24 Hours - Every Day</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">To provide excellent service for Hino customers, PT. Hino Motors Sales Indonesia provides HOTLINE or Hino Customer Care Center services.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">In addition to toll-free telephone services, Hino Customer Care can also be reached via WhatsApp, SMS and Email.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">The following are toll free telephone numbers, Whatsapp, Email, SMS Hino Customer Care Center which can be contacted 24 hours a day.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Call Center (toll free)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 0 800 100 4466<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">WhatsApp / SMS&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 0815 1900 1900</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Email&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: hino.hotline@hino.co.id<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Through the Hino Customer Care Center service customers can get a lot of information about products, sales and after sales. We also accept if there are complaints from HINO customers such as problem units, document units, warranties, etc.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Customers can also provide advice or input that is building a large HINO family.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">With this 24-hour Hino Customer Center service center, we hope to be able to help and provide maximum satisfaction to HINO's loyal customers.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">#hinoalwayswithYOU<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"\"><font face=\"Arial\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21px;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p>",
