        "sub_title": null,
        "image": "assets/uploads/articles/Mekanik_Hino_sedang_mengecek_Truk_Hino.jpg",
        "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Komitmen Hino\r\nuntuk Kenyamanan Customer,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">di\r\ntengah Pandemi COVID-19</span><br>&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;Jakarta – 20 Mei\r\n2020. Pandemi wabah Virus Corona atau COVID-19 membuat Hino terus memberikan\r\nprogram – program yang sangat dibutuhkan oleh konsumen setianya. Sebagai bentuk\r\nTotal Support Hino kepada bisnis pelanggan ditengah situasi pandemi ini, Hino\r\nmemberikan kenyamanan kepada customer dengan memberikan perpanjangan masa\r\ngaransi selama enam bulan bagi semua unit kendaaran Hino baik itu Hino Dutro,\r\nHino Ranger, Hino Profia maupun Hino Bus yang masa berakhir garansi antara\r\nbulan Maret hingga Mei 2020. Perpanjangan masa garansi 6 bulan ini akan berlaku\r\nsejak berakhirnya periode Pembatasan Sosial Berskala Besar (PSBB) di area\r\nkonsumen yang menerapkan berakhir.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">“Program ini\r\nbentuk Total Support Hino untuk selalu memberikan pelayanan terbaik kepada para\r\npelanggan setia. Dengan Extended Warranty para pelanggan akan lebih tenang dan\r\nnyaman dalam situasi saat ini, karena mereka tidak peru khawatir hangus masa\r\nwarranty dan tetap dirumah saja” ujar Santiko Wardoyo, Chief Operating Officer\r\nHMSI.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Pelanggan yang\r\nmendapatkan perpanjangan masa garansi dapat melakukan perbaikan hingga 6 bulan\r\nkedepan saat kebijakan PSBB untuk daerah yang menerapkan berakhir atau pandemi\r\nvirus corona (COVID-19) sudah pada kondisi kondusif. Pelanggan yang garansi\r\nkendaraannya berakhir pada periode tersebut, dapat menghubungi dealer terdekat\r\nuntuk mengajukan garansi dan dealer Hino akan mengeceknya dan memberikan\r\ninformasinya kepada HMSI.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Tidak hanya\r\nmemberi perpanjangan masa garansi kendaraan, para pelanggan Hino juga dapat\r\nmemanfaatkan layanan mobile Service serta program – program after sales yang\r\nsangat ekonomis yang Hino berikan dimasa pandemi Covid 19 ini. Program layanan\r\npurna jual itu antara lain, servis berkala kelipatan 10K dengan extra diskon\r\nsampai dengan 37% untuk Aki HMSI Original Part (HOP) serta gratis pengecekan,\r\ngratis filter oli, gratis jasa servis ganti oli, dan gratis layanan Home\r\nService. Pelanggan bisa mendapatkan layanan perawatan tanpa harus meninggalkan\r\nrumah. Pelanggan juga tidak perlu khawatir karena para mekanik yang dikirim\r\nmengikuti prosedur keamanan physical distancing seperti mengenakan masker dan\r\nsarung tangan, serta menjaga jarak dengan pelanggan. Sementara jika kendaraan\r\nharus dibawa ke diler untuk perawatan besar kendaraan akan dijemput untuk\r\ndiservis dan disemprotkan cairan disinfectan yang aman di workshop dealer Hino\r\nmaka akan diantar kembali dalam kondisi bersih.</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Hino juga memiliki program Servis Hemat Mobil\r\nTerawat, untuk perbaikan dan over haul diskon hingga 45% untuk suku cadang dan\r\ndiskon 20% jasa servis serta promo potongan harga Strainer Kit hanya 900.000\r\nribu. Strainer ini sangat berfungsi untuk memperpanjang filter kendaraan bahan\r\nbakar B30.</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>",
        "description_english": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Hino's Commitment to Customer Comfort, amidst the Pandemic COVID-19</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Jakarta - May 20, 2020. Pandemic outbreak of Corona Virus or COVID-19 makes Hino continue to provide programs that are needed by loyal consumers. As a form of Hino's Total Support to the customer's business in the midst of this pandemic situation, Hino provides comfort to the customer by extending the warranty period for six months for all Hino vehicle units, whether it is Hino Dutro, Hino Ranger, Hino Profia or Hino Bus, which expires between months March to May 2020. The extension to the 6-month warranty period will take effect from the end of the Large-Scale Social Restrictions (PSBB) period in the area where consumers apply.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">\"This program is a form of Hino's Total Support to always provide the best service to loyal customers. With the Extended Warranty, customers will be more calm and comfortable in the current situation, because they do not need to worry about the warranty period and stay at home, \"said Santiko Wardoyo, HMSI's Chief Operating Officer.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Customers who get an extended warranty period can make repairs up to 6 months when the PSBB policy for regions that apply ends or the corona virus pandemic (COVID-19) is in a conducive condition. Customers whose vehicle warranty expires during this period can contact the nearest dealer to submit a warranty and the Hino dealer will check it and provide information to HMSI.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Not only does it provide an extended warranty period for vehicles, Hino customers can also take advantage of the highly economical mobile service and after sales programs that Hino provided during the Covid 19 pandemic. The after-sales service program includes periodic multiples of 10K with extra discounts up to 37% for HMSI Original Part (HOP) batteries as well as free checking, free oil filters, free oil change service, and free Home Service services. Customers can get maintenance services without leaving home. Customers also do not need to worry because the mechanics sent follow physical distancing security procedures such as wearing masks and gloves, as well as keeping a distance from customers. Meanwhile, if the vehicle has to be taken to a dealer for large maintenance, the vehicle will be picked up to be serviced and sprayed with a disinfectant liquid that is safe at the Hino dealer workshop, and will be delivered back in clean condition.<br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:115%\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Hino also has a Manicured Car Savings Service program, for repairs and over hauls of up to 45% discounts on parts and 20% discounts on service services and promo discounts for Strainer Kit discounts of only 900,000 thousand. This strainer is very functioning to extend the B30 fuel vehicle filter.</font><br></p>",
